        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲股市再創紀錄新高 投資者押注聯儲會降息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"554\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6A.jVs414gegJuCeJhjcpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7516328055430167998da0e91811703c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市繼續上漲，再創紀錄新高，投資者在經濟數據表現疲軟之後，加大對聯儲會降息的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲斯托克600指數收漲0.5%，刷新紀錄高點。汽車和科技股領漲，而房地產和銀行板塊表現最弱。個股方面，西門子上漲4.2%，此前知情人士透露，該公司正在考慮剝離所持Siemens Healthineers AG多數股權中的一大部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷蘭AEX指數也創下自2月份以來的首個紀錄新高，得益於晶片巨頭艾司摩爾上漲。英國多家零售股走強，此前英國《金融時報》報導稱，出於對食品價格上漲的擔憂，財政大臣Rachel Reeves計畫將零售商從商業地產稅最高檔中剔除。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e485ec67-4bd6-3276-a9ea-c749a0926077-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經歷了過去幾個月的區間震盪後，進入第四季度，歐洲股市表現強勁。儘管如此，斯托克600指數年迄今12%的漲幅仍落後於標普500指數，因投資者對美國貿易關稅的影響保持謹慎。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"554\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/22stXkAkUjgxg7IVOnhlWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/719bdc7658e83bf2bca1a04c312cd262\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原定於周四公佈的美國首次申領失業救濟人數和工廠訂單數據因政府關門而推遲發布。在投資者尋找有關經濟的線索之際，數據發布的延遲可能會削弱市場信心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在當前這種局勢下，這些數據對於了解貨幣政策的現狀以及未來走向至關重要，」Panmure Liberum策略師Susana Cruz表示，「所以我認為這方面存在風險。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Hit Record High as Investors Bet on Fed Cuts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-162606115.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-03 01:50:45",
